## Manual Implementation Guide

The configuration guide provides detailed instructions for:

### Phase 1: Initial Setup (15 minutes)
1. Access Ghost admin at mikejones.online/ghost
2. Locate ActivityPub settings (Settings → Membership/Growth → Fediverse/Network)
3. Enable ActivityPub toggle
4. Verify "Connected" status

### Phase 2: Profile Configuration (15 minutes)
1. Set display name (e.g., "Mike Jones")
2. Verify username (should be "mike" → @mike@mikejones.online)
3. Write compelling bio emphasizing AI/ML expertise
4. Upload professional avatar/profile picture
5. Upload header image

### Phase 3: Testing (15-30 minutes)
1. Test WebFinger endpoint (optional, Ghost Pro handles automatically)
2. Search for @mike@mikejones.online from Mastodon account
3. Follow Ghost site from Mastodon
4. Publish test post
5. Verify post appears in Mastodon timeline
6. Test engagement (like, boost, reply)

### Phase 4: Content Preparation (Ongoing)
1. Draft 2-3 initial posts (AI case studies)
2. Create introduction post for Fediverse
3. Prepare hashtag strategy
4. Identify key AI/ML accounts to follow
5. Plan content calendar

**Total Estimated Time:** 30-60 minutes for initial setup and testing

